There is tension in Ikirun, headquarters of Ifelodun Local Government Area of Osun State on Thursday over the health condition of the monarch, Oba Rauf Adedeji. A source in the palace told The Nation that Oba Adedeji had been critically ill for some times but his condition worsened after he attended a function on Tuesday. Speculations have rented the community over his condition. It was gathered the monarch was rushed to a hospital in Osogbo on Thursday morning. Details shortlyâ€¦